    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I'm wondering how this could be extended to be used in other context. For instance, you might not want to have this logic on the search box but on a button when modifying a refinement list (common pattern on mobile for instance). \r\n\r\nShould we add this showLoading options on every widget/connectors? Can it be an autonomous widget? ",
